Part of the CosmoTalker Ecosystem

Oolit is the machine learning backbone of the CosmoTalker Orbitarium — an open initiative for cosmic intelligence, space education, and astrophysics Q&A systems.

"Oolit" enables space-focused reasoning, natural language understanding, and generative knowledge in astronomy and space exploration domains.

